                        h2.slider_block__subheading on the golden beach

                    .slider_block__text.slider_block__text_bottom(data-in="bottom" data-delay="200" data-out="top" data-step="2" data-time="5250").
                        We are an oceanarium on the Golden Beach. Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur
                        adipisicing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua.
